The '''Nadutheervai''' (judgement) '''Ula''' (journey) ("'''The journey to final judgement'''") is a part of [[Arul Nool]], one among the sources of [[Ayyavazhi mythology]]. This part tells about the happenings of the world in the end or at the day which [[Kaliyan|Kali]] destroys.

